    {
      "chinese": "童年的我在約10歲時，學校放了2個月的暑假。早晨時，部落的所有小朋友們，每人持著一把捕捉蝴蝶的網，身上繫著一個用來裝蝴蝶的罐子，跟隨著他們的父親前往河邊或山谷的溪流去捉蝴蝶。因為蝴蝶是從山林裡沿著峪溪飛向河川處的。",
      "ab": "Slaqi ku, ye ba wada maxal hari ka knkawas mu ciida, msange muuyas ali gndregan 2 idas mgduru rbagan. Mgrebu pnkingal kadi rraus plale ma, smiru kingal kulu ssliyan plale rnaus kana lqlaqi alang, smnegul tama daha mosa yayung Iyu ma, kyyayung lmiqu rmaus plale peni. Ado pneeyah bbuyu lmiqu kyuayu quri yayung skiya ka plale.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/02/18/04a6589546d845eb5011753d312469c7.wav",
